µC0Ghandy:µC3 Well, that was all over in one fell swoop, a few days after Kim Schmitz presented Blueboxing on the Panorama programme. A few days later, Deutsche Post installed filters so that our frequencies could no longer reach the satellite and blockers that threw you off the line. 

